## üîí Security & Compliance

### Security Features
- ‚úÖ **Type-safe config** - Prevents injection attacks
- ‚úÖ **Multi-factor auth** - OTP + SMS verification
- ‚úÖ **Audit logging** - All user actions tracked
- ‚úÖ **Rate limiting** - DDoS protection
- ‚úÖ **SQL injection prevention** - ORM-only access
- ‚úÖ **CSRF protection** - Enabled by default
- ‚úÖ **Secure headers** - HTTPS enforcement

### Compliance Standards
- üè¢ **SOC 2 Type II** compatible
- üîí **GDPR** compliant data handling
- üè• **HIPAA** ready with encryption
